    <item>
      <title>GMPC tells me that MPD playlists are not working, how to fix this</title>
      <p>
			Check if the following things are correctly configured for MPD:
  		</p>
  		<list>
  			<item><p>Is <code>playlist_directory</code> specified in MPD's configuration file?</p></item>
  			<item><p>Does the <code>playlist_directory</code> exist?</p></item>
  			<item><p>Is the <code>playlist_directory</code> readable by MPD?</p></item>
  			<item><p>Can MPD read and write the playlists?</p></item>
  		</list>
    </item>
